     'Weights', 'Offset', 'BinomialSize', 'Intercept', 'DispersionFlag', and
     'Exclude') are also accepted and forwarded to the fit.  Categorical
     predictors are not supported by the stepwise search; use ‘fitglm’ for a
     fixed model with categorical predictors.

